'''尖喙鳥'''是[[雀形目|雀形目]][[蒂泰霸鶲科|蒂泰霸鶲科]]的一種小型雀鳥，棲息於[[南美洲|南美洲]]北部山區至[[中美洲|中美洲]]南部（[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]與[[哥斯大黎加|哥斯大黎加]]）一帶。

根據分子種系發生學的研究，尖喙鳥位於蒂泰霸鶲科的基本分支<ref>{{ cite journal | last1=Ericson | first1=P.G.P. | last2=Zuccon | first2=D. | last3=Johansson | first3=U.S. | last4=Alvarenga | first4=H. | last5=Prum | first5=R.O. | year=2006 | title=Higher-level phylogeny and morphological evolution of tyrant flycatchers, cotingas, manakins, and their allies (Aves: Tyrannida) | journal=Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution | volume=40 | issue=2 | pages=471–483 | doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2006.03.031 | pmid=16678446 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1=Ohlson | first1=J. | last2=Fjeldså | first2=J. | last3=Ericson | first3=P.G.P. | year=2008 | title=Tyrant flycatchers coming out in the open: phylogeny and ecological radiation of Tyrannidae (Aves, Passeriformes) | journal=Zoologica Scripta | volume=37 | issue=3 | pages=315–335 | doi=10.1111/j.1463-6409.2008.00325.x}}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | last1=Tello | first1=J.G. | last2=Moyle | first2=R.G. | last3=Marchese | first3=D.J. | last4=Cracraft | first4=J. | year=2009 | title= Phylogeny and phylogenetic classification of the tyrant flycatchers, cotingas, manakins, and their allies (Aves: Tyrannides) | journal=Cladistics | volume=25 | issue= 5| pages=429–467 | doi= 10.1111/j.1096-0031.2009.00254.x }}</ref><ref name=ohlson2013>{{ cite journal | last1=Ohlson | first1=J.I. | last2=Irestedt | first2=M. | last3= Ericson | first3=P.G.P. | last4= Fjeldså | first4=J. | year=2013 | title=Phylogeny and classification of the New World suboscines (Aves, Passeriformes) | journal=Zootaxa | volume=3613 | issue=1 | pages=1–35 | doi=10.11646/zootaxa.3613.1.1 | pmid=24698900 |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/261371295}}</ref>，有些文獻會將其單獨歸為「尖喙鳥科」<ref name=ohlson2013/><ref>{{ cite book | editor-last1=Dickinson | editor-first1=E.C. | editor1-link=愛德華·克萊夫·迪金森  | editor-last2=Christidis | editor-first2=L. | editor2-link=萊斯利·克里斯蒂迪斯 | year=2014 | title=The Howard & Moore Complete Checklist of the Birds of the World | volume=Volume 2: Passerines | edition=4th | place=Eastbourne, UK | publisher=Aves Press | isbn=978-0-9568611-2-2 | page=17 }}</ref>。

尖喙鳥可分成4個[[亞種|亞種]]<ref name=ioc>{{cite web | editor1-last=Gill | editor1-first=Frank | editor1-link=弗蘭克·本寧頓·吉爾 | editor2-last=Donsker | editor2-first=David | year=2017 | title=Tyrant flycatchers | work=World Bird List Version 7.3 | url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/flycatchers/ | publisher=International Ornithologists' Union | accessdate=9 January 2018 | archive-date=2020-04-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424141908/https://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/flycatchers/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>：

* ''O. c. frater'' （[[菲利普·L·斯克莱特|Sclater, PL]] & {{le|奧斯伯特·薩爾文|Osbert Salvin|Salvin}}, 1868），棲息於哥斯大黎加與巴拿大西部
* ''O. c. brooksi'' （{{le|奧特蘭·邦斯|Outram Bangs|Bangs}} & {{le|托馬斯·巴柏|Thomas Barbour|Barbour}}, 1922），棲息於巴拿大東部
* ''O. c. hypoglaucus'' （Salvin & {{le|弗雷德里克·杜坎·戈德曼|Frederick DuCane Godman|Godman}}, 1883），棲息於[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]東南部、[[蓋亞那|蓋亞那]]與[[巴西|巴西]]北部
* ''O. c. cristatus'' （Swainson, 1821），棲息於巴西東南部、[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]東部與[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]東北部

